{"tid":350371,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Rem L:[A/I] Smash & Magic (5) 手機誤中1001","createTime":"2017-08-07T07:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T07:50:01.000Z","uid":117361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d40d122b55cdac63bdfd35f1ce6cbbee30423a29","tid":350371,"uid":117361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/17062105592558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F17062105592558.jpg&h=b77d898c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smash-magic.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smash-magic.com%2F&d=yom%2BsZ%2F%2Bh2NaYUktlKqFe3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ba3df217\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.smash-magic.com/</a><br />\n官方Twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/smashmagic_info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsmashmagic_info&d=yom%2BsZ%2F%2Bh2NaYUktlKqFe3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d0a646b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/smashmagic_info</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n0. 點解我刷左好耐都冇5星?<br />\nA:最高只可以抽到4星, 5星係4星升上去, 而普通角色只可以升一次星, 但係一開始4隻主角可以由2星升到4星<br />\n<br />\n1.ios可唔可以引繼到android?<br />\nA:引繼到但係鑽石帶唔走<br />\n<br />\n2.我信箱有三把鎖匙做咩唔比我拎出黎?<br />\nA:每人身上最多可以帶三把鎖匙,你未用晒就唔可以再拎出黎<br />\n<br />\n3.點解我冇得打(單人)活動?<br />\nA:要打完主線第一個島,開左第二個島先有<br />\n<br />\n4.點解我搵唔到12星合作活動?<br />\nA:要自己開房完成一次NORMAL(5星)合作活動<br />\n<br />\n5.地下城有咩武器打?<br />\nA:<a href=\"https://smash-magic.gamewith.jp/article/show/62804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmash-magic.gamewith.jp%2Farticle%2Fshow%2F62804&d=yom%2BsZ%2F%2Bh2NaYUktlKqFe3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=759c1242\" target=\"_blank\">https://smash-magic.gamewith.jp/article/show/62804</a><br />\n<br />\n6.進化要用3種虹石咁咪要儲到2046?<br />\nA:3種揀1種就得<br />\n<br />\n7.進化虹石點拎?<br />\nA:每日有得打一次虹石, 平時打關隻豬定飛飛吓定老鼠會亂入,打死佢會跌虹石, 但係記住100英雄值格升級要15粒小虹石,100英雄值裝備要7小虹石(好似係),唔好亂用小虹石"},{"pid":"51111db095d23df3e92b3ff5726840e9e78a69b8","tid":350371,"uid":117361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/350373/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/350373/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n去依個。。。"}]}